<div style="line-height: 15pt; text-indent: -96pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 96pt"><span style="font-size: 18px"><span style="font-family: 標楷體">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 杯、筷。</span></span></div>
<div style="line-height: 15pt; text-indent: -96pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 96pt"><span style="font-size: 18px"><span style="font-family: 標楷體">十四、本計畫如有未盡事宜，得隨時補充更正之。</span></span></div>
