<span style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,245,245); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; display: inline !important; font: 13px/20px Arial, 新細明體; white-space: normal; float: none; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 1px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">(二) 志工服務年資滿3年，服務時數達300小時以上者申請核發志願服務榮譽卡，志工進入收費之公立風景區、未編定座次之康樂場所及文教設施，憑志願服務榮譽卡得以免費。&nbsp;</span><br style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,245,245); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 13px/20px Arial, 新細明體; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 1px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" />
<span style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,245,245); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; display: inline !important; font: 13px/20px Arial, 新細明體; white-space: normal; float: none; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 1px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">(三) 從事志願服務工作績效優良並經認證之志工，得優先服相關兵役替代役。&nbsp;</span><br style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,245,245); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 13px/20px Arial, 新細明體; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 1px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" />
<span style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,245,245); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; display: inline !important; font: 13px/20px Arial, 新細明體; white-space: normal; float: none; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 1px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">(四) 服務時數累積達一定時數，可依相關辦法申請績優獎勵，例如：服務時數1500、2000、2500小時以上者，頒授內政業務志願服務銅、銀、金質徽章及得獎證書。&nbsp;</span><br style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,245,245); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 13px/20px Arial, 新細明體; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 1px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" />
