<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm"><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="background-color:whitesmoke"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="background-color:whitesmoke"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#212529">(1)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;村里(社區)清潔維護、環境綠美化及配合公所、環保機關辦理環保活動等。 &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />
(2)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;配合環保局辦理有關環境教育的活動。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm"><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="background-color:whitesmoke"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="background-color:whitesmoke"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#212529">-每月針對髒亂區域，街道等公共區域進行環境整潔維護3次。<br />
-由竹北市公所認養1處公園(公兒二公園)，每月隔週進行1次環境清潔及美化。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm"><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="background-color:whitesmoke"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="background-color:whitesmoke"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#212529">五、想加入志工團隊的說明：由本隊遴選合格為村里(社區)環保志工，並經志願服務基礎訓練及環保特殊訓練合格領有志願服務手冊者。 結合村里(社區)人力資源，加強環保知識技能及提昇。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm"><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="background-color:whitesmoke"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="background-color:whitesmoke"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#212529">六、服務區域：竹北市</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

